text: kalpimoun( kompir kuor an) daembi chea kar changaoulobangheanh dl mnoussaalok haey trong kaban banhchouh karvinichchhy( rveang khosa ning trauv) der . pitabrakd nasa puok del brachheang nung ayeat robsa a l laoh puokke nung ttuol tearounakamm da thngonthngor cheatibamphot . haey a l laoh mha khlangpouke meanamnach phdantatosa
